Field Detail

id

public int id
This Swarm Achievement's unique integer identification number.

orderId

public int orderId
Identifies this Swarm Achievement's position in the Swarm Achievement list. The Swarm Achievement with an orderId of 0 will be shown first in the list.

title

public java.lang.String title
The title of this Swarm Achievement that is displayed to the user in the app's achievement list and in the Swarm Notification that is shown to the user when this achievement is unlocked.

description

public java.lang.String description
The description that tells the user how to unlock this achievement.

points

public int points
The number of Swarm Points that a user will earn by unlocking this achievement.

hidden

public boolean hidden
If true, this achievement is not visible to the user in the app's list of achievements until it is unlocked. If false, this achievement is visible to the user in the app's list of achievements prior to being unlocked.

unlocked

public boolean unlocked
If true, then this achievement is unlocked and the user will see that it has been unlocked by viewing the app's achievement list. If false, then this achievement is not unlocked and the user will see that it is still locked when viewing the app's achievement list. An unlocked achievement will award a user with the applicable number of Swarm Points.

unlock

public void unlock()
Unlock the achievement and display a Swarm Notification to the user showing that this achievement was unlocked. If a user is not logged in, the call is ignored.

unlock

public void unlock(SwarmAchievement.AchievementUnlockedCB cb)
Unlock the achievement and display a Swarm Notification to the user showing that this achievement was unlocked. If a user is not logged in, the call is ignored.

Parameters:
cb - AchievementUnlockedCB callback returns true if this achievement was successfully unlocked and returns false otherwise. (null safe)
